magpie.data.utilities.generators

Class IonicCompoundGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • magpie.data.utilities.generators.BaseEntryGenerator
      • magpie.data.utilities.generators.PhaseDiagramCompositionEntryGenerator
        • magpie.data.utilities.generators.IonicCompoundGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<BaseEntry>, Options

    public class IonicCompoundGenerator
extends PhaseDiagramCompositionEntryGenerator
    Generate compositions of ionic compounds. For each compositions, it must be possible to form a charge balance compound assuming each element takes exactly one nonzero integer charge state.

    Dev Note: This class simply generates all compositions using the super class and filters out the ones that are no charge balanced. There is certainly a more efficient process.

    Usage: <min order> <max order> <number> <elements...>
    min order: Minimum number of constituents
    max order: Maximum number of constituents
    number: Maximum number of atoms in the formula unit
    elements: List of elements to include
